Title: What About Bob?
Plot: Things seem to be going well between Harry and his new flame until she walks out on him... and takes Bob's skull.  Now Dresden must find Bob and rescue him from the clutches of an old enemy.  But will Bob want to be rescued?
GuestStars: Jordan Madley,  Raoul Bhaneja,  Matthew Knight,  Jonathan Higgins,  Conrad Coates,  Daniel Kash
